      "content": "got it. one thing i've been getting asked about is how to handle more diverse hair textures or even cultural styles. like if someone has naturally curly or coily hair, or maybe they wear something more traditional like a headscarf, how does that fit into this \"professional\" look you're talking about? does that ever count as \"distracting\" in a boardroom setting?",
